Rating: 4
This was delish!!!!! I did make some adjustments thanks to some of the other cooks who have reviewed the recipe. First I cannot find clam juice or canned clams here in Holland. So I substituted 2 fish bouillon cubes in 8oz of hot water, instead of the water in the recipe I used white wine, added 2 cloves of garlic chopped and I added a touch of cayenne. Finally I had shrimp on hand so I added that to the cod. This was a lovely hearty meal with a salad. The basic recipe is a definitely a keeper.

